English For Kids
Privacy policy
This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, disclose, and protect personal information from children in compliance with the Children's Online Privacy Protection Act (COPPA) and other applicable privacy laws. We are committed to protecting the privacy and safety of children using our application.
Information that we collect
We do not collect any sensitive personal information. We only collect information permitted by law.
The types of information we may collect include automatically collected information:
Device information (e.g., device type, operating system version)
Application usage data (e.g., time spent in the app, interactions with the app screens)
Use of Information
We use the collected information for the following purposes:
To provide and improve our services to children.
To personalize the user experience and enable interactions within the application.
To analyze and monitor application usage to ensure compliance with applicable laws and regulations.
To protect the safety and security of children using the application.
Data Security
We take appropriate measures to protect the personal information of children. We implement physical, technical, and administrative safeguards to prevent unauthorized access, use, or disclosure.
Third-Party Services
Our application may contain links to third-party websites or services. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of these third parties. We encourage parents or guardians to review the privacy policies of any third-party services before allowing their child to access them.
			
			Third-Party Services that may be accessed:
Firebase SDK - data statistic and analysis service
Updates to the Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any material changes will be notified through the application or by other means to obtain parental consent if required by law. We encourage parents or guardians to review this Privacy Policy periodically.
Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy or our privacy practices, please contact us at out e-mail address.
By using our Android application for children, you acknowledge that you have read and understood this Privacy Policy and agree to its terms.